dct_description_sm: Shapefile with database compilation of clinic names, location by street address and geographically, type of roads, and incidence of disease in Malawi.
Date of information contained in database not given.
System requirements: Computer; CD drive.  Recommended software: ESRI software capable of reading the shapefile format.
